    <item>
      <title>Carpentry</title>
      <link>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/carpentry/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:47:31 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/carpentry/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;To craft or repair something with carpentry you will need to use one of the carpentry tools: Saw, Dovetail saw, Draw knife, Froe, Inshave, Scorp, Jointing plane, Moulding plane, Smoothing plane or Hammer.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Using a carpentry tool on wood equipment near an anvil will try to repair it, higher carpentry and arms lore will increase your chance of repairing the item.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To craft items with multiple materials you will need to use your carpentry tool on the secondary material first and then the logs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lumberjacking</title>
      <link>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/lumberjacking/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:47:31 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/lumberjacking/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;You can use lumberjacking for either lumbering wood or to farm crops.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To lumber wood you need to double-click any type of axe then select a tree to lumber from.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Higher lumberjacking skill and specialized crafter class will generate more logs, lumberjacking with Xarafax’s axe will double the amount of logs you get.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Having atleast 90 lumberjacking and being specialized crafter class will make you handle the axe so good that it won’t break again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Mining</title>
      <link>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/mining/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:47:31 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/mining/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;You can use mining to either mine ore or to dig for sand.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To mine ore you need to double-click a pickaxe or shovel then select a cave floor to mine from.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To dig for sand you will need to use a shovel and target sand.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Higher mining skill and specialized crafter class will generate more ores, mining with Omero’s pickaxe will double the amount of ores you get.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;blockquote&#xA;    &#xA;    class=&#34;blockquote border-start ps-3 py-1 border-primary border-4&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;Standing outside of guarded/safe zones will give you higher chance on getting zulu ores and gems aswell as generate more of all kind of ores/gems.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
